<p align="center"><span style="font-family: Arial, serif;">Exmo./a Senhor/a &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></p>
<p align="center"><span style="font-family: Arial, serif;"><b>@#NAME<br /></b></span></p>
<p>&nbsp; &nbsp;</p>
<p align="JUSTIFY"><span style="font-family: Arial, serif;"><span style="font-size: medium;"><b>Convite - </b></span></span><span style="font-family: Arial, serif;"><span style="font-size: medium;"><b>Art.&ordm; 8.&ordm; do ECPDESP</b></span></span></p>
<p align="JUSTIFY"><span style="font-family: Arial, serif;">Em virtude de relat&oacute;rio subscrito por dois professores</span><span style="font-family: Arial, serif;">, bem como da delibera&ccedil;&atilde;o da Comiss&atilde;o Permanente do Conselho T&eacute;cnico Pedag&oacute;gico do FOR.CET, de <font style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 0);">__-__-2012</font>, vimos pelo presente convid&aacute;-lo/a, nos termos do art.&ordm; 8.&ordm; do Estatuto da Carreira do Pessoal Docente do Ensino Superior Polit&eacute;cnico, </span><span style="font-family: Arial, serif;">na reda&ccedil;&atilde;o que lhe foi dada pelo Decreto-Lei n.&ordm; 207/2009 de 31 de Agosto de 2009,</span><span style="font-family: Arial, serif;">a lecionar a(s) disciplina(s) de <b>@#CURRICULAR_UNITS</b></span><span style="font-family: Arial, serif;"><b></b></span><span style="font-family: Arial, serif;">, do(s) curso(s)</span><span style="font-family: Arial, serif;"><b> @#COURSES</b></span><span style="font-family: Arial, serif;">, num total de </span><font style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 0);"><span style="font-family: Arial, serif;"><b>&laquo;Carga hor&aacute;ria&raquo;</b></span></font><span style="font-family: Arial, serif;"> horas, em regime </span><font style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 0);"><span style="font-family: Arial, serif;"><b>&laquo;Regime&raquo;</b></span></font><span style="font-family: Arial, serif;"> como</span><span style="font-family: Arial, serif;"><b> Assistente Convidado a <font style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 0);">[categoria]</font></b></span><span style="font-family: Arial, serif;">, entre </span><font style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 0);"><span style="font-family: Arial, serif;"><b>[per&iacute;odo de contrata&ccedil;&atilde;o]</b></span></font><span style="font-family: Arial, serif;"> sendo a remunera&ccedil;&atilde;o mensal il&iacute;quida a auferir no valor de </span><font style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 0);"><span style="font-family: Arial, serif;"><b>valor da remunera&ccedil;&atilde;o (valor por extenso)</b></span></font><span style="font-family: Arial, serif;">. </span></p>
<p align="JUSTIFY"><span style="font-family: Arial, serif;">Caso haja concord&acirc;ncia, agradecemos que preencha a caixa de texto abaixo.</span></p>
<p align="CENTER"><span style="font-family: Arial, serif;"><span style="font-size: medium;">Com os melhores cumprimentos,</span></span></p>
<p align="CENTER"><span style="font-family: Arial, serif;"><span style="font-size: medium;">O Diretor do FOR.CET</span></span></p>
<p align="CENTER"><span style="font-family: Arial, serif;"><span style="font-size: medium;">__________________________________</span></span></p>
<p align="CENTER"><span style="font-family: Arial, serif;">(Doutor Jos&eacute; Manuel Silva)</span></p>
